  "title": "URGENT: Medical Equipment Sales Specialist (respiratory products)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Drive sales for ventilators and enterprise solutions in Singapore</li><li>Own local accounts: product demos, solution proposals, tenders, and customer presentations</li><li>Collaborate with ICT, Application Specialists, and Engineers to deliver complete solutions</li><li>Plan and deliver end-user training, oversee project installation, and ensure successful deployment</li><li>Support marketing events, product launches, and provide market feedback</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree; 2–3 years’ experience in medical devices (ventilators, patient monitoring preferred)</li><li>Strong communication, presentation, and interpersonal skills</li><li>Self-starter, adaptable, and able to work under pressure</li><li>Team player with customer-focused mindset</li></ul><p><br />Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref68@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a></p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: John Angeline</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1544851</p>",
